{"tid":494163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU和他們合作唱哭台下愛豆團～這也許是MMA舞台上最感人的表演！","createTime":"2017-12-09T10:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T05:57:08.000Z","uid":34643,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2c27e6f681b577516597c9aaf300492d6bc10c","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_920d4469e96c240e741d41844e51c1f9/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-08/100603-562430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_920d4469e96c240e741d41844e51c1f9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-08%2F100603-562430.png&h=cc0eff0f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n多少人因為熱愛音樂或喜歡眾星捧月的感覺而選擇站在舞台上，千千萬萬的練習生中又有多少人能夠成為萬眾矚目的焦點？ 除了出名的那些人以外，剩下的人有個共同的名字「無名歌手」。<br />\n<br />\n2017Melon Music Awards中上演了一場感動無數人的場景，IU和一眾因為缺少機會登台，沒有被大眾熟知的無名歌手合作演唱了歌曲《Dear Name》。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d8cdfdcae6a8dd5d39bf634253776560/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-08/100603-562431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d8cdfdcae6a8dd5d39bf634253776560%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-08%2F100603-562431.jpg&h=a2ecab0e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nIU率先開唱，接著數十名無名歌手、歌手志願生一起合唱。 伴隨著IU甜美的歌聲，其他歌手們用「我叫梁承豪」、「我叫車光敏」等介紹短語演繹出獨特的合唱。 這些無名歌手們的介紹聽哭了台下的愛豆們，Red Velvet成員默默擦拭眼角，臉紅思春期也努力低下頭忍住眼淚，也許她們是想到了自己曾經走過的路，也許是在感歎自己的幸運。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_465527d87666af98129cb3005ebb29f4/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-08/100603-562432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_465527d87666af98129cb3005ebb29f4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-08%2F100603-562432.jpg&h=c93fd4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bb6e7ee31618bf3e0b2ef3ec6101004f/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-08/100603-562433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bb6e7ee31618bf3e0b2ef3ec6101004f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-08%2F100603-562433.jpg&h=bca60ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8822306b43ace0d342e2889ebb569156/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-08/100603-562434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8822306b43ace0d342e2889ebb569156%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-08%2F100603-562434.jpg&h=cd554123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e3dbb8e783bd448f00475ff0ce71b2c9/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-08/100603-562435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e3dbb8e783bd448f00475ff0ce71b2c9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-08%2F100603-562435.jpg&h=8be0bc53&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n無名歌手們也許不能通過這首歌曲就走紅，但希望他們能堅持自己的夢想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QKtHufXng2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQKtHufXng2Y&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d88bfc99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QKtHufXng2Y</a>"},{"pid":"e48700042aa609f856a33da4fbf09a7be8c58eb8","tid":494163,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多<br />\n宋慧喬我老婆"},{"pid":"50d05675599712457814b84a84b11648c86f0c04","tid":494163,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"韓國競爭真係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5256dfc44b602044233b4edc61f60938613627","tid":494163,"uid":36236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:49:33.000Z","msg":"要好似韓國最強歌姬咁真係萬中無一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f47badf822c906cf5c697b45440f53d0858591","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"live片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sq9czx3EZcI?t=775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsq9czx3EZcI%3Ft%3D775&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fd6dc441\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sq9czx3EZcI?t=775</a>"},{"pid":"8538023e190035207f0b8136c4f418870db3fb52","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要好似韓國最強歌姬咁真係萬中無一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做好自己, 自然會成功"},{"pid":"b64c01ea776ecf96f8c5f0cfb6cc1519c222c0ee","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講咁多<br />\n宋慧喬我老婆</blockquote><br />\n今日兩公婆都有去iu concert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQmes7WUMAAMu-B.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQmes7WUMAAMu-B.jpg%3Aorig&h=657e0ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQmes7VUQAAX3Bb.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQmes7VUQAAX3Bb.jpg%3Aorig&h=14679a2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8779e7d8603c903ecb72300af9ab38326d544bad","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"song song<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fmava1x7wcj30h00l9401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fmava1x7wcj30h00l9401.jpg&h=364402bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6cc98d19cd32e7908751a03aac5161f84b35815","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>song song<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fmava1x7wcj30h00l9401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fmava1x7wcj30h00l9401.jpg&h=364402bc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\niu有兩餸飯"},{"pid":"3a2b5621dd9e7469a448560d1b7413be9a32cc08","tid":494163,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實雙宋飯 個飯字係點解<br />\n韓文唔太識"},{"pid":"439fa460f01d6be16271f83255883b459266156f","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實雙宋飯 個飯字係點解<br />\n韓文唔太識</blockquote><br />\n粉絲英文叫fans，因此諧音就叫「飯」。"},{"pid":"36cb1f4c62558075ebd7c8cf1693e188dc3862a0","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQp2tRXUQAAunzk.jpg:orig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQp2tRXUQAAunzk.jpg%3Aorig&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7d1e39b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQp2tRXUQAAunzk.jpg:orig</a><br />\nre encore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.宋仲基和宋慧喬站起來打算走的時候前面的人和他們說還沒結束呢 他們驚訝得眼睛睜大了 然後坐下來繼續看了哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n2.宋宋cp旁邊坐著朴率美(昨天IU ins發IUTV的時候她還評論了天使)<br />\n<br />\n3.安安可的時候偷看了一下宋宋 宋慧喬看著舞台臉上帶著媽媽微笑 有種很欣慰很開心的感覺哈哈哈 ​<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朴率美<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fmb0kebsmaj30sc0scjsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fmb0kebsmaj30sc0scjsn.jpg&h=e9097fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那樣小小的身體里怎麼會有那麼巨大的能量呢<br />\n那些深沉的想法到底是從幾歲開始有的呢<br />\n雖然不能具體的說出是哪些點<br />\n但是常常會覺得羡慕，感到安慰，又會覺得有些刺激到我<br />\n我還年輕（？）的時候要是有這種朋友就好了~我會邊思考我的人生，或許還會有某種成長也說不定~<br />\n不管怎麼說！<br />\n今天真的特別帥氣<br />\n我的眼睛和耳朵都非常享受<br />\n以後也會一直一直為你應援的<br />\n明天最後一場演唱會也要加油！<br />\n這麼說顯得有點陌生啊&hellip;kk<br />\n本來想直接走的，不過後來還是鼓起勇氣去後台照了認證照然後紅著臉跑出來了<br />\nIU演唱會#小知恩 再見啦"},{"pid":"f1d7ac4a853965f65567f298c6692725956cd1e9","tid":494163,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"咸左"},{"pid":"f8076ecf577fcfc047534c1cd33fd06eaad253ce","tid":494163,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>song song<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fmava1x7wcj30h00l9401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fmava1x7wcj30h00l9401.jpg&h=364402bc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\niu有兩餸飯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770d14efcc45a19e8ed76b746fcd1179ed152d37","tid":494163,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"即刻係youtube搵左黎睇  都幾感動"},{"pid":"bb0977142657293e1a6c6699e256a8bc247522d7","tid":494163,"uid":87818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻係youtube搵左黎睇  都幾感動</blockquote><br />\n現場聽應該起晒雞皮"},{"pid":"a6f63ceafa874f77901277db238bf28bec38d083","tid":494163,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻係youtube搵左黎睇  都幾感動</blockquote><br />\n好似話係想叫人多d關注下練習生"}]}